%N A396554 Numbers k such that EulerPhi(psi(k)) is not a power of 2, where psi = A002322 is the reduced totient function.
%C A396554 Numbers k such that psi(k) is not in A003401.
%C A396554 Numbers k such that the range of chi contains non-constructible numbers for some Dirichlet characters chi modulo k.
%H A396554 Wikipedia, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Constructible_number">Constructible number</a>.
%H A396554 Wikipedia, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dirichlet_character">Dirichlet character</a>.
%o A396554 (PARI) ispower2(n) = (bitand(n,n-1) == 0)
%o A396554 isA396554(n) = !ispower2(eulerphi(A002322(n))) \\ see A002322 for its program
%Y A396554 Cf. A002322, A003401, A396553 (complement), A396555 (prime terms).
